project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eHowever, just because you\u0026#39;re dining at home, doesn\u0026#39;t mean you can\u0026#39;t create an authentic Spanish experience with all of the right dishes. Refreshing your crockery with the right-sized plates and bowls will elevate meal times.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d.jpg\" alt=\"Terracotta tapas dishes\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qJYaHRtuSQQFjSwkC9Tq9d-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-m